        "created_at": "2019-08-20T19:05:02.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I bought a couple of bottles of the 1975 Lafleur on release - at $10.95 because the store couldn\u2019t sell it at $14.95.  I served one of them at a friend\u2019s 40th birthday, and while it was tannic, it was sound and not at all like the wine Tom had.  I will serve the second bottle at my friend\u2019s 50th birthday.</p>\n<p>David<br>\n<img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/5/f/5f9033708df32dc270ee51eddb75e100b29419af.jpeg\" alt=\"1975 Lafleur.JPG\" data-base62-sha1=\"dDoj8Vot30KG5KT0WR7NcnICJEr\" width=\"1224\" height=\"1632\"></p>",
